      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Basil Falcinelli</b>\n</p><p><b>Basil Falcinelli</b>,<br />\na programmer in the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Internet_security\">internet security</a>, \n<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Internet_privacy\">Internet privacy</a> and <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cryptocurrency\">cryptocurrency</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open-source_model\">open source</a> community <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> affiliated with <i>ReQrypt.org</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, also involved in computer chess. \nHe introduced and published a <a href=\"/Linux\" title=\"Linux\">Linux</a> port of the <a href=\"/Gull\" title=\"Gull\">Gull 3</a> chess engine <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>, \nwhich subsequently evolved to <a href=\"/Gull#LazyGull\" title=\"Gull\">LazyGull</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>, further incorporating his <a href=\"/Syzygy_Bases#Fathom\" title=\"Syzygy Bases\">Fathom</a> <a href=\"/Syzygy_Bases\" title=\"Syzygy Bases\">Syzygy tablebase</a> probing tool <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2015\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2016\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2016</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Basil_Falcinelli&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015\">2015</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Basil_Falcinelli&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2015\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=58071\">Gull 3 (Linux port) released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Basil Falcinelli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 28, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=58157&amp;start=4\">Re: c++ class or a c wrapper for the syzygy egtb</a>] by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Basil Falcinelli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 08, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Syzygy_Bases#Fathom\" title=\"Syzygy Bases\">Fathom</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=58299\">Gull 3 Linux+Syzygy and Fathom released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Basil Falcinelli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 20, 2015</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2016\">2016</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Basil_Falcinelli&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2016\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=60906&amp;start=17\">Re: Syzygy and draw by repetition</a> ] by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Basil Falcinelli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 23, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Syzygy_Bases#Fathom\" title=\"Syzygy Bases\">Fathom</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=61559&amp;start=11\">Re: syzygy users (and Ronald)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Basil Falcinelli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 01, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Syzygy_Bases#Fathom\" title=\"Syzygy Bases\">Fathom</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=61594&amp;start=13\">Re: Crafty 25.1 Release</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Basil Falcinelli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 05, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Crafty\" title=\"Crafty\">Crafty</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=62078&amp;start=7\">Re: What about Gull?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Basil Falcinelli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 11, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=62378&amp;start=9\">Re: Help for Syzygy probe?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Basil Falcinelli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 07, 2016</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Basil_Falcinelli&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/basil00/\">basil00 · GitHub</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/basil00/Gull\">GitHub - basil00/Gull: Gull chess (Linux/Mac port) - The LazyGull Chess Engine</a></dd>\n<dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/basil00/Fathom\">GitHub - basil00/Fathom: Syzygy TB probe tool</a></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Basil_Falcinelli&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/basil00/\">basil00 · GitHub</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://reqrypt.org/home.html\">ReQrypt</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=58071\">Gull 3 (Linux port) released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Basil Falcinelli</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 28, 2015</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/basil00/Gull\">GitHub - basil00/Gull: Gull chess (Linux/Mac port) - The LazyGull Chess Engine</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/basil00/Fathom\">GitHub - basil00/Fathom: Syzygy TB probe tool</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301153450\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.009 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.010 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 93/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 202/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:6161-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301153450 and revision id 14596\n -->\n"
